# 301 Permanent Redirects: old transliterated URLs â†’ new English URLs
# Static rules (exact match) first, then dynamic rules (splat) per CF docs

# Note: 
# Don't try to be smart (like I did!) and merge these into a single /subpath*
# rule. This is problematic cause because it would be greedy and match things
# it shouldn't. For instance, adding a /liqa-aram-tv* rule would match:
# - /liqa-aram-tv
# - /liqa-aram-tv/
# - /liqa-aram-tv/?bla=foo
# - /liqa-aram-tv-2026 // <-- this is incorrect
#
# We probably don't have such cases here, but just in case

